Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.19,0:22:27.03,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,1000)}{\blur3}(WIRED……)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.36,0:22:31.16,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)}{\blur3}舞う蝶のようにヒラリ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.28,0:22:35.00,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}{\blur3}宙に漂う不可思議な光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.45,0:22:39.04,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,500)}{\blur3}ここはどこか別の世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.21,0:22:44.17,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1035)\fad(150,1000)}{\blur3}落下する速度は變わらない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.88,0:22:46.88,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1035)\fad(220,500)}{\blur3}Cut the Rope
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.55,0:22:50.51,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)}{\blur3}Cut the Rope
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.51,0:22:52.10,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}頭をめぐる數值は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.10,0:22:54.22,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,250)}{\blur3}螺旋を描き急上昇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.22,0:22:57.77,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}重大な過ちにも氣づかずに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.77,0:23:01.23,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人から人へとつながる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.23,0:23:04.86,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}淡く青藍に輝くWire
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.86,0:23:08.82,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}とてもきれいでまるで絹の糸
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.82,0:23:12.87,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}これが運命という鎖なのか
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.87,0:23:16.33,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}探して でも 絡まって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.33,0:23:18.08,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}だどり著けない
